dune-mm-amg
===========

A DUNE module that lets you read linear systems from matrix market files and
the solves it using the aggregation AMG that comes with dune-istl.

Dependencies
------------

dune-mm-amg depens on the following software packages

- dune-istl >=2.3 module http://dune-project.org
- CMake
- A C++11 standard conforming compiler, e.g. GNU C >=4.4

